### Get User
### ============================================

### Get user (success)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/123

###

### Get user (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/999

###

### Get user (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/

###

### ============================================
### Create User
### ============================================

### Create user (success)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "age": 25
}

###

### Create user (duplicate email)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "duplicate@example.com",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "age": 25
}

###

### Create user (invalid email)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "age": 25
}

###

### Create user (age too young)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "minor@example.com",
  "name": "Minor User",
  "age": 15
}

###

### Create user (missing name)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "age": 25
}

###

### Create user (name too short)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "name": "AB",
  "age": 25
}

